49:	    def create(self, name=None, container=None, attributes=None, num_objects=1):
50:	        if num_objects > 1:
51:	            threads = [
52:	                self.create_thread(
53:	                    self.create, name="%s_%s" % (name, i), container=container, attributes=attributes, num_objects=-1
54:	                ) for i in range(num_objects)
55:	            ]
56:	            return self.run_threads(threads)
57:	        elif num_objects == -1:
58:	            self = Folder(self.auth)
59:	
60:	        if not name:
61:	            if not self.name:
62:	                raise AssertionError('Must supply a name property.')
63:	            name = self.name
64:	        if not container:
65:	            if not self.container:
66:	                raise AssertionError('Must supply a container property.')
67:	            container = self.container
68:	        if not attributes:
69:	            if self.attributes:
70:	                if not isinstance(attributes, list):
71:	                    raise TypeError('Attributes must be a list.')
72:	                attributes = self.attributes
73:	
74:	        dn = container + '\\' + name
75:	
76:	        self._logger.log('Creating policy with DN "%s".' % dn)
77:	        if self.auth.preference == ApiPreferences.websdk:
78:	            policy = self.auth.websdk.Config.Create.post(dn, ConfigClass.policy, attributes or []).object
79:	        elif self.auth.preference == ApiPreferences.aperture:
80:	            policy = self.auth.aperture.ConfigObjects.Policies.post(name, container).object
81:	        else:
82:	            raise FeatureError.invalid_api_preference(self.auth.preference)
83:	
84:	        self.load(policy)
85:	        if self.dn:
86:	            self._logger.log('Folder DN is %s.' % self.dn)
87:	        else:
88:	            raise ValueError('DN not created as expected.')
89:	
90:	        return self

15:	        :type username: str

18:	        dn = folder.dn + "\\" + name
19:

28:	                {'Name': 'Password', 'Type': 'string', 'Value': password}

30:	        ).result
31:
